\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $c(g)$
\end_inset

 is the number of chromosomes for genotype 
\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $\mu(g)$
\end_inset

 is the probability of sampling a mutant read given the genotype 
\begin_inset Formula $g$
