\begin_inset Formula $b$
\end_inset

 of these are mutants is then
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray*}
p(b|d,\boldsymbol{\psi},\phi,t) & = & \text{Binomial}(\cdot|d,\xi(\boldsymbol{\psi},\phi,t)
\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

