\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
To finish off the model we need a prior for 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi$
\end_inset

.
 In the absence of any knowledge we use a continuous prior.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
We assume 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

